{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ae8df23a-f5a1-4e48-b657-4ca5ac80035d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ae8df23a-f5a1-4e48-b657-4ca5ac80035d@1.pkg/1772597702554/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597703055", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ae8df23a-f5a1-4e48-b657-4ca5ac80035d@1.pkg/1772597702554/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597703055"}, "identifier": "ae8df23a-f5a1-4e48-b657-4ca5ac80035d", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;拥有积极的人生态度&rdquo; 的知识点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>：小李和小王面对相同的登山环境，因态度不同做出了不同选择，体现了不同人生态度对行为的影响，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：小李以积极态度看待困难，将其视为挑战自我的机会，最终坚持攀登，说明积极态度能让人看到希望、激励行动，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>：小王因消极态度放大困难，选择半途放弃，体现了消极态度的负面影响，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：&ldquo;环境是决定成功的唯一因素&rdquo; 错误，成功取决于态度、努力等多种因素，环境只是其中之一，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>在一次登山活动中，面对陡峭的山路，小李觉得 &ldquo;这是挑战自我的好机会，坚持下去就能看到山顶的风景&rdquo;，于是咬牙向上攀登；小王却认为 &ldquo;山路太险，肯定无法登顶，不如趁早放弃&rdquo;，最终半途折返。两人的不同选择告诉我们（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>面对同一情境，不同的人生态度会导致不同的行为</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>积极的人生态度能让人在困难中看到希望，激励行动</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>消极的人生态度容易使人放大困难，进而退缩放弃</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>环境的好坏是决定人们能否成功的唯一因素</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）在一次登山活动中，面对陡峭的山路，小李觉得 “这是挑战自我的好机会，坚持下去就能看到山顶的风景”，于是咬牙向上攀登；小王却认为 “山路太险，肯定无法登顶，不如趁早放弃”，最终半途折返。两人的不同选择告诉我们（ ）①面对同一情境，不同的人生态度会导致不同的行为②积极的人生态度能让人在困难中看到希望，激励行动③消极的人生态度容易使人放大困难，进而退缩放弃④环境的好坏是决定人们能否成功的唯一因素", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ae8df23a-f5a1-4e48-b657-4ca5ac80035d@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984697928", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②③</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②④</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③④</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>在一次登山活动中，面对陡峭的山路，小李觉得 &ldquo;这是挑战自我的好机会，坚持下去就能看到山顶的风景&rdquo;，于是咬牙向上攀登；小王却认为 &ldquo;山路太险，肯定无法登顶，不如趁早放弃&rdquo;，最终半途折返。两人的不同选择告诉我们（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>面对同一情境，不同的人生态度会导致不同的行为</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>积极的人生态度能让人在困难中看到希望，激励行动</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>消极的人生态度容易使人放大困难，进而退缩放弃</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>环境的好坏是决定人们能否成功的唯一因素</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {